                            </div>
                            <div class="royalties">Regalías: 10% artista</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="nft-actions">
                            <button class="btn btn-primary">Comprar NFT</button>
                            <button class="btn btn-secondary">Vista Previa</button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="nft-card">
                    <div class="nft-badge">MusicCard</div>
                    <div class="nft-image">
                        <div class="placeholder-nft">🎶</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="nft-info">
                        <h3>Momentos Musicales #23</h3>
                        <p class="artist">Colección Vol. 1</p>
                        <div class="nft-details">
                            <span class="edition">45/500 disponibles</span>
                            <span class="rarity">Raro</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="price-section">
                            <div class="price">
                                <span class="algo-price">15 ALGO</span>
                                <span class="usd-price">~$25 USD</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="royalties">Regalías: 8% artista</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="nft-actions">
                            <button class="btn btn-primary">Comprar NFT</button>
                            <button class="btn btn-secondary">Vista Previa</button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="nft-card">
                    <div class="nft-badge">Nuevo</div>
                    <div class="nft-image">
                        <div class="placeholder-nft">🎼</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="nft-info">
                        <h3>Schubert Collection</h3>
                        <p class="artist">Goulnara Galimchina</p>
                        <div class="nft-details">
                            <span class="edition">120/1000 disponibles</span>
                            <span class="rarity">Común</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="price-section">
                            <div class="price">
                                <span class="algo-price">8 ALGO</span>
                                <span class="usd-price">~$13 USD</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="royalties">Regalías: 7% artista</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="nft-actions">
                            <button class="btn btn-primary">Comprar NFT</button>
                            <button class="btn btn-secondary">Vista Previa</button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="nft-card presale">
                    <div class="nft-badge">🔥 Preventa</div>
                    <div class="nft-image">
                        <div class="placeholder-nft">🎆</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="nft-info">
                        <h3>Proyecto Enmanuel NFT</h3>
                        <p class="artist">Enmanuel Vivas</p>
                        <div class="nft-details">
                            <span class="edition">0/250 (Preventa)</span>
                            <span class="rarity">Edición Especial</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="price-section">
                            <div class="price">
                                <span class="algo-price">25 ALGO</span>
                                <span class="usd-price">~$42 USD</span>
                                <span class="discount">30% OFF</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="royalties">Regalías: 12% artista</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="nft-actions">
                            <button class="btn btn-primary">Pre-orden</button>
                            <button class="btn btn-secondary">Más Info</button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="wallet-info">
                <div class="wallet-card">
                    <div class="wallet-card-content">
                        <h2>💼 Cómo Comprar</h2>
                        <div class="steps">
                            <div class="step">
                                <span class="step-number">1</span>
                                <p>Conecta tu wallet de Algorand (Pera Wallet recomendado)</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="step">
                                <span class="step-number">2</span>
                                <p>Selecciona el NFT que deseas comprar de nuestra colección</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="step">
                                <span class="step-number">3</span>
                                <p>Confirma la transacción en tu wallet de forma segura</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="step">
                                <span class="step-number">4</span>
                                <p>¡Disfruta tu NFT musical con regalías automáticas!</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <button class="btn wallet-connect">Conectar Wallet</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
        </div>
    </main>
</body>
</html>